WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.251 --> 00:00:07.131
Mr. Lin walks through a misty forest.

2
00:00:14.427 --> 00:00:16.800
He pauses among the mist.

3
00:00:29.525 --> 00:00:32.962
Startled, he flings his sleeve up.

4
00:00:32.962 --> 00:00:36.400
A close-up shows his uneasy face.

5
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:24.300
He walks deeper into the mist.

6
00:01:36.325 --> 00:01:39.200
He turns and walks on.

7
00:02:02.850 --> 00:02:07.175
He walks into the garden, its gate open.

8
00:02:22.250 --> 00:02:25.150
His eyes widen as he looks around.
